nodes.text: Neebray mantas were a type of flying creature found throughout the galaxy, dwelling on planets like Tatooine, moons like the Rishi Moon, and even in the void of space in the Kaliida Nebula. The monstrously large neebray mantas found in space fed on space gases. Baby neebrays could be found on Rugosa and in space. They were biologically related to tibidees and mynocks. Neebrays had large teeth and spotted patterns on their skin in adulthood.
